    <h1>5-3-1 Workout Scheduler and Guide</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        5-3-1 is a workout that is designed for people who may only have that 30 minute lunch break to workout during. The 5-3-1 workout is designed around
        four main lifts, bench press, squat, shoulder press, and dead lift. These four lifts are the core of the workout and if you want suplemental lifts
        you can choose from anything you would like.
    </p>
