        <h2>Getting started</h2>
        <p>
            Getting started with 5-3-1 is easy. Get a gym membership, go to your local weightroom, or buy some weights!
            Then get your butt up and go! That is the hardest part about the 5-3-1 workout design, getting up and going. But you can
            do it!!
        </p>
    </div>
